        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Medium- and Heavy-Duty Electric Vehicle Infrastructure Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Environmental Protection Agency to establish a rebate program that encourages the purchase and installation of electric vehicle charging equipment for medium-duty electric vehicles and heavy-duty electric vehicles.</p>]]>
        </text>
